## Required flow

1. Claim escalate tasks when Adam asks you to check the queue or when control-plane status indicates attention is needed.
2. Inspect claimed task content before acting.
3. Discuss decisions with Adam when human judgment is needed.
4. Enqueue durable follow-up work rather than doing AFK execution yourself.
5. Attach evidence or decision artifacts when useful.
6. Complete or fail the held task when the escalation is resolved.

